data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET!! Buyer's financing fell through. Their loss = your gain! Welcome to your ideal home! This 4-bedroom, 2 full-bath gem spans 2,042 sqft, offering ample space for your growing needs. Recent renovations have breathed new life into this property, including fresh flooring, a recent roof within a few years and a state-of-the-art HVAC system - ensuring your comfort and peace of mind But that's not all - the motivated seller is eager to make a deal,  making this an excellent opportunity for homebuyers to secure their dream home.
